## Examples

Trivial:

```elixir
~f"![X,Y]: X | Y => Y | X" |> prove
```

requires $\mathfrak{b}$:

```elixir
~f"![X,Y]: X | Y = Y | X" |> prove
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{leibniz1}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X,Y]: (l @ (X | Y) @ (Y | X))
).
""" |> prove
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{leibniz2}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X,Y]: (l @ (X | Y) @ (Y | X))
).
""" |> prove
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{leibniz3}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X,Y]: (l @ (X | Y) @ (Y | X))
).
""" |> prove
```

```elixir
res = ~p"""
#{andrews}
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X,Y]: (a @ (X | Y) @ (Y | X))
).
""" |> prove
```

requires $\mathfrak{b}$ and $\xi$:

```elixir
res = ~f"(^[X,Y]: X | Y) = (^[X,Y]: Y | X)" |> prove
```

